$ Oracle Manageability Monitor Process (MMON)

The *Manageability Monitor process* collects memory statistics from the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/SGA periodically stores
them as snapshots in the → development/databases/Oracle/Automatic-Workload-Repository[Automatic Workload Repository] (AWR).
-
The default period is 60 minutes. This duration can be changed.

MMON also performs Automatic Database Diagnostic Monitor (ADDM) analysis. If one of the metrics exceeds a given threshold value, MMON issues an alert.

MMON is a → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/processes/background[background process].

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/processes/background/MMNL
